title: Adventure Time - Pixel Princesses GN (2013, Dgtl, BlurPixel-Empi
description:
OH MY GLOB U GUYZZZ, it's a brand new Adventure Time graphic novel! Promotional info - "Princess gatherings aren't always tea parties and doilies, there is a lot more to being a Princess that one might think. Danielle Corsetto (GIRLS WITH SLINGSHOTS) and Zack Sterling return with an adventure where some of our favorite princesses learn what it really takes to be a princess, while learning to respect each other for their unique outlooks on life." It's B&W and 196 pages as well.

Thanks to BlurPixel-Empire, and please seed - enjoy! :-)
